<title>USA: Patriot American makes acquisitions.</title>
<headline>Patriot American makes acquisitions.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1996-12-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Patriot American Hospitality Inc said Monday it reached an agreement with Resorts Limited Partnership, Carefree Resorts Corp and Resorts Services Inc to acquire these entities and their assets.</p>
<p>Total anticipated value of the transaction is about $210 million, in a combination of cash, debt assumptions and units in Patriot's operating partnership, the statement says.</p>
<p>The agreement is subject to the approval of certain limited partners of Resorts Limited Partnership, a statement from Patriot American said.</p>
<p>Assets of these entities include the entire management organization and the interests in four, four-star and five-star Carefree resort properties, the statement said.</p>
